title: Tournament of Chompions: FINALS with Paul Rust
itunes:title: Tournament of Chompions: FINALS with Paul Rust
description:
The finale of Munch Madness 2017: Chicken Fight has guest Paul Rust (Netflix’s Love) returning to help crown a Chompion. Will Popeyes continue to dominate the competition? Can Wingstop keep alive its Cinderella streak? Does the winner of Fat Chance Kitchen stand a chance in the main competition? One thing’s for sure: Commissioner Susser will throw some curve balls that make Mitch and Wiger mad. It all comes down to this!
Make YOUR chompion predictions @ www.feralaudio.com/chompions2017

Want more Doughboys? Check out our Patreon!: https://patreon.com/doughboys
